Interface Updatable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bot, CardMenu, Engine, MainMenu, Options, Particle, Racer, Renderer, Results, Selector
    public interface Updatable
    This interface allows the classes that implement it to be able to recieve updates from the game master.

    • Method Summary

      Modifier and Type Method Description
      void update​(long deltaTime)
      Updates this so that it assumes a state an amount of time in the future.
